{"about_the_game":"<strong>WHAT'S THIS? A REMAKE OF ASTEROIDS FROM 1979?</strong><br><br>Well, as asteroids are one of the <u>best games of all time</u>, we wanted to make a worthy successor 40 years after the initial release of the classic game. Bigwig Flint is developed over 5 years with lots of love put into every level, made for <strong>hardcore gamers</strong>.<br><br>But it <i>isn't a remake</i> even though it still has the sexy triangle as the hero and there are vicious asteroids and spaceships. So yes, it is a top down shooter but not an asteroids clone - it's Kanselsprot Entertainment <strong>paying tribute to a classic game</strong> with their own take on a top down shooter.<br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong><i>- Advance through multifarious levels<br>- Fight with Epic Bosses<br>- Collect XP and level up your weapons and skills<br>- Enjoy highly responsive controls<br>- Find hidden levels and bonuses<br>- STEAM Achievements<br>- Experience the in-house created physics based universe</i></strong></ul><br><strong>FOR:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong><i>- brutal hardcore, retro gaming-lovers<br>- asteroids lovers<br>- non-asteroids lovers</i></strong></ul><br><strong>NOT FOR:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong><i>- weak-minded<br>- haters</i></strong></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"SHARPSHOOTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1248960/1157ab93e4b85b4507d96e7ca8e09d3bcd95480c.jpg"},{"name":"SNIPER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1248960/8e48ef0d70b2e7b595fa335f5cd9c83fd2bc4b12.jpg"},{"name":"CHAINGUNNER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1248960/717aae698f7b5868701c81f34260243d20530503.jpg"},{"name":"BACKFIRER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1248960/da8d70a8492659ffbf0b893bbbfd65ff93f25853.jpg"},{"name":"GAME FINISHER","path":